title: Cajun Style Blackened Sea Bass
ingredients: ['2 tablespoons paprika', '2 teaspoons cayenne pepper', '1 1/2 teaspoons ground white pepper', '1 1/2 teaspoons ground black pepper', '1 tablespoon salt', '2 teaspoons onion powder', '2 teaspoons garlic granules', '1 teaspoon dried thyme', '1 teaspoon dried oregano', '4 (175g) fillets sea bass', '340g butter, melted']
